      "coverage": "No distributed tracing mentioned",
      "gaps": [
        "No trace spans for the full payment lifecycle: receive → fraud check → Stripe charge → DB write → respond",
        "Cannot correlate a slow payment to which leg (fraud, Stripe, DB) caused the delay",
        "No trace propagation to the internal fraud detection service"
      ]
    },
